		<atom:link rel="payment" title="Flattr this!" href="https://flattr.com/submit/auto?user_id=11729&amp;popout=1&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fcocktailpodcast.de%2F2012%2F03%2F16-cocktailbitter%2F&amp;language=de_DE&amp;category=audio&amp;title=%2316+%26%238211%3B+Cocktailbitter&amp;description=Das+Salz+in+der+Suppe+ist+f%C3%BCr+uns+Cocktailliebhaber+der+Cocktailbitter.+Diesmal+widmen+wir+uns+diesen+bitteren+Tinkturen%2C+die+so+manchen+Drink+abrunden+oder+erst+spannend+machen.+Im+ausgehenden+20....&amp;tags=Angostura%2CAngostura+Aromatic+Bitter%2CBitter+Truth%2CBitters%2CBrooklyn+Lamp%2CCelery+Bitters%2CCharles+Schuhman%2CCharles+Schuhmann%2CCharles+Schuman%2CCharles+Schumann%2CCocktailbitter%2CFee+Brothers%2CGrapefruit+Bitters%2CManhattan%2CMartini%2CMozart+Chocolate+Bitters%2COld+Fashioned%2COld+Fashionned%2COrange+Bitters%2CPeychaud+Bitters%2CRose+Petal+Water%2CRosenbl%C3%BCtenwasser%2CRosenwasser%2CTBT+Berlin+Bitters%2CTBT+Orange+Flower+Water%2CThe+Bitter+Truth+Traveller%27s+Set%2CW%C3%BCrbitter%2Cblog" type="text/html" />
