		<atom:link rel="payment" title="Flattr this!" href="https://flattr.com/submit/auto?user_id=11729&amp;popout=1&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fcocktailpodcast.de%2F2011%2F12%2F14-weihnachtscocktails%2F&amp;language=de_DE&amp;category=audio&amp;title=%2314+%26%238211%3B+Weihnachtscocktails&amp;description=Als+kleines+Sahneh%C3%A4ubchen+f%C3%BCr+die+Feiertage+haben+wir+uns+durch+die+K%C3%A4lte+des+ersten+Schnees+gek%C3%A4mpft%2C+um+uns+ein+paar+passende+Drinks+zu+genehmigen.+Bevor+wir+uns+aber+an+einem...&amp;tags=Alexander%2CAlexander%E2%80%99s+Sister%2CAmarula%2CAperitif%2CBrandy+Alexander%2CChristian+Schroff%2CCinarula%2CClement%2CCreme+de+cacao%2CCreme+de+menthe%2CDaktari%2CDill%2CDill-Aquavit%2CEggnogg%2CEi%2CEier%2CEierlik%C3%B6r%2CEierpunsch%2CFeuerzangenbowle%2CGalliano%2CGiffard%2CHot+Buttered+Rum%2CIrish+Coffee%2CMarius+Kleiner%2CMedizin%2CMuskat%2CNachtisch%2CNegroni%2COld+Monk%2CPinienkerne%2CPlagiat%2CPrincess+royal+Mary%2CRye%2CSan+Francisco%2CWeihnachten%2CWinter%2Cblog" type="text/html" />
