		<title>#12 &#8211; Long Island Iced Tea / Filler</title>
		<link>http://cocktailpodcast.de/2011/08/12-long-island-iced-tea-filler/</link>
		<comments>http://cocktailpodcast.de/2011/08/12-long-island-iced-tea-filler/#comments</comments>
